### Test Google Meet with Shared Calendar
### This test verifies that the Google Meet integration works with the shared calendar

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@studentToken = YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Test Google Meet Link Generation (Should now work with shared calendar!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/google-meet
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Shared Calendar Test Session",
  "description": "Testing Google Meet with shared calendar (swapev192@gmail.com)",
  "duration": 60,
  "platform": "google-meet",
  "startTime": "2024-12-25T10:00:00Z"
}

### Expected Results:
### - Real Google Meet link should be generated
### - URL format: https://meet.google.com/xxx-yyyy-zzz (with hyphens)
### - Link should work when opened in a browser
### - Meeting should appear in the shared calendar
### - Check server logs for success messages

### 2. Test with Different Duration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/google-meet
